'''球棒'''是[[棒球|棒球]]、[[壘球|壘球]]運動中，[[打擊手|打擊手]]用來擊球的[[棒子|棒子]]。重量最重不超過1公斤，長度最長不超過1067mm，直径70mm以下<ref name="Bleacher">{{cite web|url=http://bleacherreport.com/articles/589660-size-matters-top-10-biggest-in-mlb#/articles/589660-size-matters-top-10-biggest-in-mlb/page/2|title=Size Matters: Top 10 "Biggest" In MLB History|author=Jenn Zambri|work=Bleacher Report|access-date=13 September 2015|archive-date=2021-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211115154127/https://bleacherreport.com/articles/589660-size-matters-top-10-biggest-in-mlb#/articles/589660-size-matters-top-10-biggest-in-mlb/page/2|dead-url=no}}</ref>。依材质的不同，有木棒、竹棒、鋁棒和碳纤维棒之分。[[職業棒球|職業棒球]]及[[成棒|成棒]]、[[青棒|青棒]]賽事大多使用木棒，[[青少棒|青少棒]]、[[少棒|少棒]]以及[[壘球|壘球]]則以鋁棒為主。也有供兒童專用的[[泡棉|泡棉]]材質球棒。

除了做為運動器材，球棒也被用作攻擊武器。根據[[塔斯社|塔斯社]]於2015年的報導，在棒球運動不流行的[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]，2014年全年卻可賣出50萬支球棒，許多駕駛人在車上備有球棒以在遭遇行車糾紛時使用<ref>{{cite news |author1=吳美依 |title=俄羅斯「年銷50萬支球棒」卻只賣出1顆棒球　警：不打棒球只打人  原文網址: 俄羅斯「年銷50萬支球棒」卻只賣出1顆棒球　警：不打棒球只打人 |url=https://www.ettoday.net/news/20211116/2124687.htm |accessdate=2021-12-19 |publisher=ETtoday新聞雲 |date=2021-11-16 |archive-date=2021-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211219154317/https://www.ettoday.net/news/20211116/2124687.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 材料和製造 ==
球棒的材質可能是木或是金屬合金（一般會是[[鋁合金|鋁合金]]）。大部份木棒是由[[梣树|梣木]]所製，也有用[[枫属|枫木]]、[[山核桃属|山核桃木]]、[[白桦|白桦]]、[[黄桦|黄桦]]或[[竹|竹]]製造。山核桃木因為其重量較重，會讓揮棒的速度變慢，因此較少使用，自從1997年引入第一個美國職棒大聯盟認可的枫木球棒系列後，越多人使用枫木球棒<ref name="SciAm1">{{cite web|last1=Patterson|first1=Brittany|title=Baseball Bats Threatened by Invasive Beetle|url=https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/baseball-bats-threatened-by-invasive-beetle/|website=Scientific American|publisher=Scientific American|access-date=21 November 2017|archive-date=2021-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523113435/https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/baseball-bats-threatened-by-invasive-beetle/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一個使用的打者是[[多倫多藍鳥|多倫多藍鳥]]的[[喬·卡特|喬·卡特]]<ref name="Canadian Sports Magazine 2008, p. 8">''Canadian Sports Magazine'', Vol. 2, No. 3, August 2008, p. 8, (Publication Mail Agreement #40993003, Oakville, ON)</ref>。[[貝瑞·邦茲|貝瑞·邦茲]]用枫木球棒在2001年打破了2001年單一球季的全壘打記錄，在2007年打破了生涯全壘打記錄<ref name="Canadian Sports Magazine 2008, p. 8" />。因為枫木球棒破裂的比例漸漸提高，美國職棒大聯盟在2010年時開始進行檢驗，並在小聯盟的比賽禁止使用特定型號的枫木球棒<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2010/09/20/129985928/-the-well-is-effectively-dead?print=1|title=The Well Is Effectively Dead|date=20 September 2010|work=NPR.org|access-date=13 September 2015|archive-date=2012-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905110411/http://www.npr.org/blogs/thetwo-way/2010/09/20/129985928/-the-well-is-effectively-dead?print=1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = MLB bans use of many maple bats in minor leagues; safety concerns cited | date = 11 September 2012 | url = http://aol.sportingnews.com/mlb/story/2010-03-01/apnewsbreak-many-maple-bats-get-banned-minors | work = Archive.is | access-date = 14 July 2017 | url-status = bot: unknown | archive-url = https://archive.today/20120911101218/http://aol.sportingnews.com/mlb/story/2010-03-01/apnewsbreak-many-maple-bats-get-banned-minors | archive-date = 11 September 2012 }}</ref>。

製作球棒時，製造商會在機械強度較弱的一面放上球棒的標誌<ref name="woodbat.org"/>，減少球棒破裂的機率<ref name="woodbat.org"/>，有可能在擊球時可以傳遞更多的能量到球上<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseball-fever.com/archive/index.php/t-24217.html|title=Wood bats - on which "side" should the ball's impact be?|work=baseball-fever.com|access-date=14 July 2017|archive-date=2016-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729054056/http://www.baseball-fever.com/archive/index.php/t-24217.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在水平揮棒時，標誌應該會面對地面或是面對天空<ref name="woodbat.org">{{cite web|url=http://www.woodbat.org|title=Wood science and how it relates to wooden baseball bats|work=woodbat.org|access-date=13 September 2015|archive-date=2021-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210705174609/https://www.woodbat.org/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。若依這個握棒以及擊球的方式，球棒的韌性較高，也比較不會斷裂<ref name="mlb.mlb.com">{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081209&content_id=3708319&vkey=hotstove2008&fext=.jsp|title=Safety tests for maple bats mandated|work=Major League Baseball|access-date=14 July 2017|archive-date=2014-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730053611/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20081209&content_id=3708319&vkey=hotstove2008&fext=.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

